title.narrative: EA Regional Transport , Trade and Development Facilitation Project (Second Phase of Program)

description.narrative: The objective of the Project is to improve the movement of people and goods, digital connectivity and access to social services to communities at designated locations along selected sections of the Eldoret-Nadapal/Nakodok road corridor.
